<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>물품 입출고 내역</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <!-- 헤더 -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                <i data-lucide="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">물품 입출고 내역</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">모든 물품의 입고 및 출고 기록을 확인합니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 메인 콘텐츠 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <!-- 필터 및 검색 -->
            <div class="p-4 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center bg-slate-50 gap-4">
                <div class="flex gap-2 w-full md:w-auto overflow-x-auto pb-2 md:pb-0">
                    <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-slate-800 text-white">
                        전체
                    </button>
                    <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100">
                        입고
                    </button>
                    <button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100">
                        출고
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 w-full md:w-auto">
                    <div class="relative w-full md:w-64">
                        <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                        <input 
                            type="text" 
                            placeholder="물품명 검색..." 
                            class="w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 테이블 -->
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[800px]">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">일시</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">구분</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">물품명</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">수량</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">담당자</th>
                            <th class="p-4 font-medium">비고</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                        <!-- 내역 1 -->
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">2026-03-03 14:30</td>
                            <td class="p-4">
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-down-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                                    입고
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">주사기 (10ml)</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                                <span class="text-green-600">+100</span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">박관리</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">정기 발주 입고</td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- 내역 2 -->
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">2026-03-03 11:15</td>
                            <td class="p-4">
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-red-100 text-red-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                                    출고
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">알코올 솜</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                                <span class="text-red-600">-5</span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">이간호</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">제1진료실 요청</td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- 내역 3 -->
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">2026-03-02 16:45</td>
                            <td class="p-4">
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-down-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                                    입고
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">타이레놀 정</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                                <span class="text-green-600">+500</span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">박관리</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">긴급 발주 입고</td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- 내역 4 -->
                        <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">2026-03-02 09:20</td>
                            <td class="p-4">
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-red-100 text-red-800">
                                    <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                                    출고
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">A4 용지</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                                <span class="text-red-600">-2</span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">김원무</td>
                            <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500">원무과 보충</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 페이지네이션 -->
            <div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-center">
                <nav class="flex items-center gap-1">
                    <button class="p-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 disabled:opacity-50" disabled>
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-left" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </button>
                    <button class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-medium bg-indigo-600 text-white">
                        1
                    </button>
                    <button class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50">
                        2
                    </button>
                    <button class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50">
                        3
                    </button>
                    <button class="p-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50">
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </button>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 아이콘 초기화
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
